snippet.title: TUFU | Menus And All Customizations
snippet.description:
Follow up to the last video....every car is completely customizable, a lot of things had to be fixed, code as well as assets. This took a lot of manual work.

You can freely create profiles and share them with others, restart your progression or from time to time switch to a different progress. All of the menues are finished.
